---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contacto · AMPD" description="Ponte en contacto con la Asociación Madrileña de Psicología del Deporte.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Hablemos</span>
      <h1>¡Ponte en<br/><em>contacto</em>!</h1>
      <p class="lead">Si quieres colaborar con nosotros, obtener más información o inscribirte en la asociación, rellena el formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo lo antes posible.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <aside class="contact-info reveal">
          <div class="info-block">
            <span class="info-label">Síguenos en</span>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/AMPDMadrid" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="info-value">Twitter / X →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="info-block">
            <span class="info-label">Ubicación</span>
            <span class="info-value">Madrid · España</span>
          </div>

          <div class="info-block">
            <span class="info-label">Quieres asociarte</span>
            <a href="/hazte-socio" class="info-value">Cuotas y ventajas →</a>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <form class="contact-form reveal" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Mensaje enviado (demo).');">
          <p class="form-note">* Indica un campo obligatorio</p>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label>Nombre <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" required placeholder="Primero" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label>Apellido</label>
              <input type="text" placeholder="Apellido" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label>Correo electrónico <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <input type="email" required placeholder="tu@email.com" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label>Comentario <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <textarea rows="6" required placeholder="Cuéntanos en qué podemos ayudarte..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
            Enviar
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .page-hero h1 { margin: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .page-hero h1 em { color: var(--flame); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
  .lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.4rem);
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .contact-section {
    border-top: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: 5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .info-block {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .info-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--flame);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .info-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  a.info-value:hover { color: var(--flame); }

  .contact-form {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }
  .form-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .form-field label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.7);
  }
  .req { color: var(--flame); }
  .form-field input,
  .form-field textarea {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.3);
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .form-field textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.3);
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--flame);
  }
  .form-field input::placeholder,
  .form-field textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.4); }

  .contact-form button {
    align-self: flex-start;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
